     futex                693     45  4317.231     0.000     6.230   500.077     21.98%
     poll                 300      0  1040.109     0.000     3.467   120.928     17.02%
     clock_nanosleep        1      0  1000.172  1000.172  1000.172  1000.172      0.00%
     ppoll                360      0   872.386     0.001     2.423   253.275     41.91%
